# Agent Rules: Genshin Planner

This file defines the behavior and conventions for AI agents interacting with this repository.

## Documentation Files Map
When asked to view, review, or update documentation .md files in the repository, you can locate them at:
- **General Project Overview & Features**: [README.md](file:///Users/daxiok/projects/genshin-planner/README.md) (root directory)
- **Local Dev & Supabase Setup**: [SETUP.md](file:///Users/daxiok/projects/genshin-planner/SETUP.md) (root directory)
